pr_title: Remove javadoc for setter method when setter method is not generated

timeline.message: Remove javadoc for setter method when setter method is not generated

timeline.bodyText: We probably need better docs here? But not critial
timeline.author: jianghaolu

replies.bodyText: I think these docs are from Swagger and not sure why it changed. I will go look at the swagger.
replies.author: srnagar

replies.bodyText: I think we used to print "The {} property" when Swagger doc is missing but I don't know why this is changed either
replies.author: jianghaolu

replies.bodyText: Yeah, if it was empty we would have generated "The {} property" but in this case swagger has non-empty doc. So, we just use that. It might be difficult to determine if the doc is insufficient from swagger.
replies.author: srnagar

replies.bodyText: It appears that swagger of testservice changed.
replies.author: weidongxu-microsoft
